--------------------------------
Antispam module for phpgroupware
--------------------------------

WARNING:
 
 - The author assumes that the user has sucessfully installed Spamassassin
   (http://www.spamassassin.org/dist/sql/README can help you about the
   SQL configuration)

 - NOTE:
	the preferences  db   is:	phpgroupware <or phpgw's main db> 
	the preferences table is:	phpgw_antispam

Thanks to "Chris Weiss" for the feedback, bug reports and help!

I'd lile have feedback and bug reports to improve the module!

